body.description: Staying organized has never been easier or more stylish! Our Packing cubes come in a set of three measuring 4"L x 5.25"W x 2"H, 8"L x 4"w x 4.5"H and 6"L x 10.5"W x 2.5"H. Each cube features a mesh top panel, making contents easy to view, and dual zippers to allow for quick access to your items. Each cube includes a soft fabric handle, making it easy to re-arrange them within a diaper bag, suitcase or purse. And they are machine washable! Our Packing cubes can be used together or individually, allowing them to be the ultimate organizers for traveling and life on the go!

manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Packing cubes can be used together in a larger bag or suitcase, or individually in a smaller bag! About Our Brand Itzy Ritzy takes pride in offering stylish solutions to every day parenting challenges. Our product line includes diaper bags, breastfeeding scarfs, reusable snack bags, shopping cart covers and much more. From multi-purpose designs that empower to chic prints that inspire, we've reinvented practical luxury for modern families around the world while remaining true to our core vision of keeping things simple. Itzy Ritzy Set of 3 Packing Cubes Perfect for a Boss Backpack, Itzy Mini Backpack or Dream Collection Bag! This set of three packing cubes make it easy to stay organized! Each cube features a mesh top panel for easy viewing, dual zippers to make it easy to access your items, and a soft fabric handle to make each bag easy to remove or rearrange within your diaper bag. Best of all, our packing cubes are machine washable! Use them together or individually to remain stylishly organized while on the go! Packing cubes measure: 4" L x 5.25" W x 2" H 6" L x 10.5" W x 2.5" H 8" L x 4" W x 4.5" H Designed to fit perfectly in both an Itzy Ritzy Boss Backpack Diaper Bag and an Itzy Mini Diaper Bag Backpack The packing cubes also fit into each bag in our Dream Collection A mesh top panel makes it easy to see what is stored in each cube Dual zippers allow for quick access to your goods and make it easy to utilize every inch of packing space Each bag includes a soft fabric handle to easily grab and rearrange

Three Sizes of Cubes Per Set Small Cube The smallest packing cube makes a great "parent cube" - it's the perfect size for storing lotion, hand sanitizer, keys, first aid items, lip balm, makeup and contact solution! Medium Cube The mid-size cube is great for storing extra clothes, bibs and blankets. The soft sides of the cube make it easy to take advantage of its full capacity since you aren't confined to stiff sides! Large Cube The largest packing cube is the perfect size for storing diapers, wipes, wet bags and diaper creams. In fact, you can store everything you need for a diaper change in this cube so it's all in one place when that time comes!

Packing Cubes Inside an Itzy Mini Backpack Diaper Bag The perfect fit with pockets to spare! These packing cubes fit inside an Itzy Mini diaper bag and still allow space for extra items to be placed in the front zippered pocket and the exterior pockets.

Packing Cubes Inside an Itzy Ritzy Boss Backpack Diaper Bag The large capacity of our Boss Backpack diaper bag greatly benefits from the organization these packing cubes provide! Use our packing cubes to keep the main compartment organized (with room to spare!) and utilize the inner and outer pockets to keep the rest of your essentials in place and easily accessible.

A Place For Everything! Small Cube The smallest cube in this set measures 4" L x 5.25" W x 2" H. Each packing cube features dual zippers and a mesh top panel so you can easily see and access the items you are storing! Medium Cube The mid-size cube measures 6" L x 10.5" W x 2.5" H. A soft fabric handle on each packing cube makes it easy to grab them and rearrange them inside of your diaper bag! Large Cube The largest cube in this set measures 8" L x 4" W x 4.5" H. These packing cubes are machine washable!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 23, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Good quality, small, but price was too high
reviews.reviewText: I thought these were nicely made with good materials and a very attractive print. I just felt they were much smaller than I realized for the price. I returned them and bought larger ones for 1/3rd of the price that are less nice but have better value

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 15, 2023
reviews.reviewText: To preface, floral cube set is 2 years old.The tan set is 8 months old, both with constant use.Both sets have been washed when dirty, they fit so much! All of the cubes pictured are in my diaper bag right now. They’ve been stretched tho the limit, and the zippers never failed yet.I use the little ones for toiletries, emergency kit things, and the other is baby medicines. You can easily fit 3 2 oz bottles and syringes in one, sometimes I’ll squeeze a 4th in.Definitely would recommend

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on March 9, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Perfect for travel!
reviews.reviewText: Got these for our first trip with my 10 mo old. They held all his stuff and made it quick for easy access to them! After we got back from the trip, I keep one in his bag for extra clothes, one in the car with a quick kit of everything I may need and use the smaller one as a medicine kit. Plus, the pattern is super cute!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 8, 2020
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars A mommy must!
reviews.reviewText: I absolutely love these packing cubes!!! I have a fawn design backpack diaper bag that I for a while felt was too small. I was considering buying a bigger bag because I felt that everything was a mess and I couldn’t fit it all in. I’m huge on organization and this was driving me crazy! Well I bought these packing cubes as a last resort and I’m absolutely in love! Not only is everything organized but it all fits in perfectly AND I now have room for more!!! I love the design and quality of the bags. The sizes are perfect. They aren’t very structured which I think is key. The fact that they are so malleable allows you to fit so much in! I’m totally going to order the new leopard ones next! This is an absolute mommy must!

I love these packing cubes for the diaper bag. I also have a set for my oldest kids daycare bag. I use them for clothes, snacks, and first aid supplies. I've had my first set for 3 years now with almost daily use and they're still great. The fabric has softened up but that's not an issue at all. I highly recommend if you're looking for packing cubes.

reviews.reviewTitle: Poor Quality and a bag was missing
reviews.reviewText: Just like the title- cheap cheap quality. $50 for what? Not worth it, not itzy ritzy quality. Pattern was cute, it’s worth 1 start.
Amei as cores. Não é tão pequeno como disseram! Claro, melhor seria se fosse maior. Não vale o preço cobrado, porém não me arrependo de tê-lo adquirido por ser muito lindo e quase perfeito!

reviews.reviewTitle: Los amo, no volveré a empacar sin estos cubos
reviews.reviewText: Amo, amo, amo estos cubos. Pensé que no les cabría mucho cuando los ví pero la verdad les cabe bastante! Empaqué 5 cambios de ropa para bebé en el cubo grande,14 pañales talla 2 y un wet bag en El cubo mediano y bastantes medicinas en el cubo pequeño. Me ayudó bastante para organizar la maleta de mi bebé y reducir el espacio en la pañalera.

reviews.reviewTitle: Way better than I thought they’d be.
reviews.reviewText: So cute and they help to keep me organized in my itzy ritzy mini diaper bag. The colours are vibrant and they are durable.
